          "line_ref": "L29"
        }
      ],
      "caveat": "The immunopeptidomic analysis was performed in mouse models, and while robust, may not perfectly reflect the human tumor microenvironment."
    },
    {
      "claim_id": "C02",
      "claim": "The mechanism by which intratumoral mRNA sensitizes tumors to ICI is dependent on the induction of Type I interferon signaling pathways.",
